data.description: Call today to see this beautiful single-story home built in 2021. This home has open floor plan. The kitchen offers island, pantry, Appliances including REFRIGERATOR, RANGE, MICROWAVE, DISHWASHER, WASHER, DRYER, granite counter tops, tile back splash, wine rack and breakfast area. Large family room open to kitchen and breakfast area. Master Suite has walk in closet, master bath with shower and double sinks. Additional amenities include cold REFRIGERATED AIR, SHUTTERS, 2 car garage, utility room and doorbell camera. Front landscaping has turf, tree, bushes and bubble drip system. Backyard has covered patio and no back neighbors. This home is close to restaurants, shopping and easy access to loop 375 and has two community parks.
